verbose_text: Although no changes were observed in melanosome phagocytic activity (data not shown) or autophagic activity (XREF_FIG F, G) in NHEKs after the application of isolated melanosomes, their significant increase in ET-1 synthesis in contrast to no changes in the expression of SCF and alphaMSH (data not shown) was interesting (XREF_FIG C, D).
evidence: ET-1 synthesis in contrast to no changes in the expression of SCF
